{"tid":1093882,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"今日考英文聆聽 真係好撚嬲","createTime":"2019-04-06T01:21:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-06T12:45:06.000Z","uid":138732,"like":16,"dislike":90,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0c3fee4ccc3102f3f1b1be81c1c9f1c852c5fbc7","tid":1093882,"uid":138732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T01:21:30.000Z","msg":"是咁的 小妹今日就考英文聆聽卷啦 <br />\n<br />\n跟住要用收音機呢啲石器時代科技<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係小妹平時都係用開iphone上下連登玩下抖音咁<br />\n<br />\n邊有用過咩收音機喎<br />\n<br />\n於是坐喺個位到研究咗好耐都唔識用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗起連登啲人話:「2019年喇仲用收音機 係咪on9？」<br />\n<br />\n加埋小妹嗰時已經好撚嬲 <br />\n<br />\n於是即刻叫個監考員過嚟屌柒佢一獲甘 然後頭也不回地就走咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗返起真係覺得自己好型好先進好有批判思考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7408b49914905a52603cbcdb8f7690c4da983b90","tid":1093882,"uid":161159,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T01:23:11.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a116a4f313edfd03594abea2af9209838baa980c","tid":1093882,"uid":138732,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7408b49914905a52603cbcdb8f7690c4da983b90","tid":1093882,"uid":161159,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T01:23:11.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T01:40:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69ef05b33cfba9744a6790196fd446272a0629e0","tid":1093882,"uid":242917,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T01:42:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4efb4cc5d72ecd9f321253e78aeb8d26f7334935","tid":1093882,"uid":176442,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T01:44:45.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"8b3a17c78766a770ae883d